<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 09:13:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>印度 莫迪与普京的莫斯科峰会被视为中国阴影下两国关系的关键</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india-modis-moscow-summit-with-putin-seen-key-ties-chinas-shadow-2024-07-03/</link><description>分析人士表示，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪预计在几天内访问俄罗斯，这可能有助于打消人们的担忧，即新德里与西方过于接近，与莫斯科距离越来越远，从而将空间让给了中国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 08:54:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india-modis-moscow-summit-with-putin-seen-key-ties-chinas-shadow-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>习主席表示中方支持哈萨克斯坦加入金砖国家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-supports-kazakhstan-joining-brics-president-xi-says-2024-07-03/</link><description>中国官方媒体周三报道称，中国国家主席习近平表示，他支持哈萨克斯坦加入金砖国家集团，因为这个发展中国家正在考虑进一步扩张，以与它认为已经过时的西方主导的世界秩序相抗衡。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 08:34:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-supports-kazakhstan-joining-brics-president-xi-says-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>联合国报告称中国在人工智能专利竞赛中处于领先地位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/china-leading-generative-ai-patents-race-un-report-says-2024-07-03/</link><description>联合国周三的数据显示，中国在聊天机器人等生成式人工智能发明方面远远领先于其他国家，申请的专利数量是最接近的竞争对手美国的六倍。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 08:06:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/china-leading-generative-ai-patents-race-un-report-says-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>外汇分析师表示，印度卢比兑人民币套利交易在美国大选结果之前仍将具有吸引力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/india-rupee-chinese-yuan-carry-trade-hold-appeal-until-us-election-outcome-fx-2024-07-03/</link><description>交易员和外汇分析师表示，将世界上两个人口最多的国家的货币相互进行交易一直是套利交易者的热门选择，并且至少在今年晚些时候美国大选结果出来之前，这种吸引力将保持下去。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 07:48:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/india-rupee-chinese-yuan-carry-trade-hold-appeal-until-us-election-outcome-fx-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>德国汽车业敦促欧盟降低对中国制造汽车的关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/german-car-industry-urges-eu-drop-tariffs-china-made-cars-2024-07-03/</link><description>德国汽车工业协会(VDA)敦促欧盟委员会取消对中国制造的电动汽车征收的关税，这是在周四关税生效前影响谈判的最后努力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 07:10:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/german-car-industry-urges-eu-drop-tariffs-china-made-cars-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>随着贸易争端升级，欧盟各国政府对中国电动汽车关税犹豫不决</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-governments-waver-over-chinese-ev-tariffs-trade-spat-escalates-2024-07-03/</link><description>欧盟国家在是否支持对中国制造的电动汽车征收额外关税的问题上犹豫不决，突显出布鲁塞尔在为其最大贸易案争取支持方面面临的挑战，而北京则威胁要进行大范围的报复。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 06:04:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-governments-waver-over-chinese-ev-tariffs-trade-spat-escalates-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>据英国《金融时报》报道，欧盟拟对中国特木和希因征收进口关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/eu-takes-aim-chinas-temu-shein-with-proposed-import-duty-ft-reports-2024-07-03/</link><description>英国《金融时报》周三援引三名知情人士的话报道称，欧盟正在制定计划，对从 Temu、Shein 和 AliExpress 等中国在线零售商购买的廉价商品征收关税。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 04:19:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/eu-takes-aim-chinas-temu-shein-with-proposed-import-duty-ft-reports-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>日本当局保持观望，日元跌至新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-defensive-amid-lower-yields-yen-hovers-near-38-year-trough-2024-07-03/</link><description>周三，日元兑美元汇率跌至38年新低，兑欧元汇率创历史新低，日元继续贬值，日本官员在干预风险中基本上保持观望。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 02:12:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-defensive-amid-lower-yields-yen-hovers-near-38-year-trough-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示中国服务业活动增速创8个月新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-services-activity-growth-hits-8-month-low-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-07-03/</link><description>周三的一项私营部门调查显示，受新订单增长放缓拖累，中国服务业活动增速为八个月来最慢，六月份信心跌至四年低点，这表明需要更多经济刺激措施。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 01:50:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-services-activity-growth-hits-8-month-low-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯普京和中国习近平将在哈萨克斯坦举行安全峰会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-arrives-kazakhstan-russia-china-dominated-sco-summit-2024-07-03/</link><description>俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京和中国国家主席习近平将于周三在欧亚安全与防务俱乐部峰会上会面，莫斯科和北京将其视为对抗美国及其盟国影响力的工具。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 01:31:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-arrives-kazakhstan-russia-china-dominated-sco-summit-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称中国在其海岸附近扣押渔船</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-china-seizes-fishing-boat-near-chinese-coast-2024-07-02/</link><description>台湾海岸警卫队表示，周二晚间，中国官员登上并扣押了一艘在靠近台湾控制岛屿的中国海岸附近作业的台湾渔船，并将其带到中国港口，紧张局势进一步升级。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 22:37:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-china-seizes-fishing-boat-near-chinese-coast-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，埃克森-赫斯仲裁小组即将组建</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/exxon-hess-arbitration-panel-nears-formation-sources-say-2024-07-02/</link><description>两位知情人士告诉路透社，最后一名成员已被选入三人仲裁小组，旨在解决埃克森美孚针对雪佛龙以 530 亿美元收购赫斯公司提出的索赔。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 21:12:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/exxon-hess-arbitration-panel-nears-formation-sources-say-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>意大利扣押运往利比亚的中国制造军用无人机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/italy-seizes-chinese-made-military-drones-destined-libya-2024-07-02/</link><description>意大利海关警察和海关机构周二表示，意大利当局拦截并扣押了两架中国制造的军用无人机，这些无人机的目的地是利比亚，伪装成风力涡轮机设备。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:33:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/italy-seizes-chinese-made-military-drones-destined-libya-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>智库称，美国军事基地附近的新古巴雷达站可能有助于中国间谍活动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/new-cuban-radar-site-near-us-military-base-could-aid-china-spying-think-tank-2024-07-02/</link><description>古巴正在建设一个新的雷达站，可能能够监视美国附近的​​关塔那摩湾海军基地，这是华盛顿智库利用卫星图像发现的，这是该国监视能力的最新升级，长期以来一直被认为与中国有关。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:32:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/new-cuban-radar-site-near-us-military-base-could-aid-china-spying-think-tank-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，柏林将阻止曼恩能源解决方案公司的燃气轮机部门向中国出售</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/berlin-block-sale-man-energy-solutions-gas-turbine-unit-china-sources-say-2024-07-02/</link><description>三名知情人士周二告诉路透社，德国将阻止大众汽车子公司曼能源解决方案公司燃气轮机部门向一家中国公司出售的计划。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 15:45:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/berlin-block-sale-man-energy-solutions-gas-turbine-unit-china-sources-say-2024-07-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>